song.title: Julia '96
song.info:
"This track was written in 1995 by me and now it was fully reworked and by the way: I've cut the first part of song, cause "Julia" must bring only bright tones into your heart, and nothing more ;) and the first part is too sad for it. If you liked first part, listen to Julia '95
To be enjoyed :)"
